<section xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>28-3806</num>
  <heading>Attorney’s fees.</heading>
  <text>With respect to a consumer credit sale or direct installment loan the agreement may provide for the payment by the consumer of reasonable attorney’s fees not in excess of 15% of the unpaid balance of the obligation.</text>
